summary: Explore digital resources including profiles like Jan Hein Hoogstad, a self-taught software architect with a PHD in Philosophy and founder of Varias. He focuses on improving team performance through technology, AI, and shared spaces. Jan also organizes the Superconnectors event, connecting startups with influential people in the Dutch tech ecosystem.
